@NAME:	IsNumber
@STATE:	CLIENT/SERVER
@DESC:	{
	Checks whether the given value is a number.
	Returns `true` if the value is of type number, otherwise `false`.
}
@PARAM:
	v <any> : The value to check.
@RETURN:
	<boolean> : `true` if `v` is a number, `false` otherwise.
@EXAMPLE:
```lua
print(IsNumber(42))       -- Output: true
print(IsNumber("42"))     -- Output: false
print(IsNumber(3.14))     -- Output: true
```